Shipping Forecast Recorder Installer
Version: 0.1
Release Date: 2025-11-28
Lines of Code: ~2900

Components:
- install.sh (main orchestration)
- lib/colors.sh (256-color terminal support)
- lib/ui.sh (interactive UI components)
- lib/checks.sh (system validation)
- lib/packages.sh (multi-distro package management)
- lib/config.sh (configuration management)
- lib/rollback.sh (error handling & rollback)
- lib/tailscale.sh (Tailscale authentication)

Features:
✓ Interactive configuration with sensible defaults
✓ Multi-distribution support (Debian, Ubuntu, Fedora, Arch)
✓ Professional 256-color terminal UI
✓ Tailscale integration with QR code authentication
✓ Automatic rollback on installation failures
✓ Multiple modes: interactive, silent, update, dry-run, diagnose
✓ Progress tracking and validation
✓ Comprehensive error handling
✓ Configuration persistence

Tested on:
- Raspberry Pi OS (Debian-based)
- ARM64 architecture
- Python 3.11.2
